definitions.definition: Of an individual, having any of a variety of inherent conditions (in a species with distinct sexes) in which one's sex characteristics differ from those of a typical male and female ; for example, having sex characteristics relating to both male and female sexes .
A person who can get pregnant and also impregnate someone else.
